{
  "video_id": "LTnI7cmpDZI",
  "title": "What makes life complete? | Gaur Gopal Das | TEDxMITP",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Sanketh Sampara Reviewer: Queenie Lee"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 8191.000000000001,
      "end_time": 11990.0,
      "text": "One of my friends in Mumbai, a Gujarati gentleman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12631.0,
      "end_time": 19220.0,
      "text": "he purchased a very expensive, high-end, upmarket car:"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20385.0,
      "end_time": 26477.0,
      "text": "a slick, posh, yellow Lamborghini."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28580.0,
      "end_time": 32272.0,
      "text": "You know cars are expensive in Mumbai, things can&#39;t get more expensive than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32272.0,
      "end_time": 35220.0,
      "text": "If you have watched this Hindi movie \"Deewar,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35615.0,
      "end_time": 37816.0,
      "text": "Amitabh Bachchan and Shashi Kapoor."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37816.0,
      "end_time": 39830.0,
      "text": "Amitabh Bachchan talking to Shashi Kapoor:"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39830.0,
      "end_time": 46340.0,
      "text": "(Hindi) \"I have a car, a house, money, and servants. What do you have?!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 47114.0,
      "end_time": 49199.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 49200.0,
      "end_time": 51150.0,
      "text": "Amitabh replies, \"I have a mother.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51150.0,
      "end_time": 54618.0,
      "text": "(English) The rhyme of today has changed, ladies and gentlemen."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54618.0,
      "end_time": 59818.0,
      "text": "Amitabh says, (Hindi) \"I have Lamborghini, I have a Jaguar, I have a Bentley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59818.0,
      "end_time": 63528.0,
      "text": "I have a BMW, I have a Rolls-Royce."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63528.0,
      "end_time": 65184.0,
      "text": "What do you have?!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65184.0,
      "end_time": 67733.0,
      "text": "(English) Shashi Kapoor says, \"I have parking space!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67733.0,
      "end_time": 69253.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69253.0,
      "end_time": 72673.0,
      "text": "(Applause) (Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72673.0,
      "end_time": 77803.0,
      "text": "Here in Mumbai, parking space is more expensive than cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 78182.0,
      "end_time": 82710.0,
      "text": "This friend of mine, a Gujarati, purchased a yellow Lamborghini"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83170.0,
      "end_time": 85545.0,
      "text": "and called me up and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85545.0,
      "end_time": 88298.0,
      "text": "\"Would you like to bless my car?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88298.0,
      "end_time": 89898.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 89898.0,
      "end_time": 94328.0,
      "text": "Now in India, everything gets blessed: babies, marriages, job contracts;"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 94638.0,
      "end_time": 96277.0,
      "text": "all the stuff gets blessed."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 96277.0,
      "end_time": 100319.0,
      "text": "\"So would you like to bless my car, we&#39;ll go for an inaugural drive with it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100901.0,
      "end_time": 102571.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Well, it&#39;s a Lamborghini."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102571.0,
      "end_time": 105331.0,
      "text": "When do swamis get to bless Lamborghinis? Come here."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 105331.0,
      "end_time": 106848.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106848.0,
      "end_time": 109344.0,
      "text": "The gentlemen drove to our temple in the Lamborghini,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109344.0,
      "end_time": 111814.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"We&#39;ll go on a 15-minutes drive.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 111814.0,
      "end_time": 114139.0,
      "text": "I sat in the passenger seat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 114139.0,
      "end_time": 116658.0,
      "text": "and the gentleman sat in the driver&#39;s seat, obviously;"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 116659.0,
      "end_time": 117739.0,
      "text": "he was driving."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 117739.0,
      "end_time": 118749.0,
      "text": "I was the first one!"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118749.0,
      "end_time": 121679.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t even have his wife to drive first."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121679.0,
      "end_time": 123476.0,
      "text": "Choose your career wisely, you know!"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 123476.0,
      "end_time": 126706.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 129453.0,
      "end_time": 131825.0,
      "text": "This gentleman, we went on a drive."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131825.0,
      "end_time": 134785.0,
      "text": "The car encountered a traffic light at Peddar Road."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135245.0,
      "end_time": 137917.0,
      "text": "And there was some car standing there;"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137917.0,
      "end_time": 141387.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t even remember what model, I&#39;m sitting in a Lamborghini."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141387.0,
      "end_time": 143104.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m sitting there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 143104.0,
      "end_time": 148450.0,
      "text": "and this gentleman in the next car, he turned his head around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148450.0,
      "end_time": 150714.0,
      "text": "and his eyes were, like, big."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 150715.0,
      "end_time": 155765.0,
      "text": "Never in the streets or roads of Mumbai had he seen a slick, yellow Lamborghini."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155765.0,
      "end_time": 161135.0,
      "text": "And his eyes went even bigger when he saw me sitting inside the car!"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161135.0,
      "end_time": 163480.0,
      "text": "You should have seen the expression on his face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163480.0,
      "end_time": 166269.0,
      "text": "he was, like, \"Swamiji, you too?!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166270.0,
      "end_time": 167560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 167560.0,
      "end_time": 171796.0,
      "text": "I wanted to pull the windscreen down and say, \"Man, this is not my car."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 171796.0,
      "end_time": 175206.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m the blessing man, 15 minutes blessing and it&#39;s done!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 175206.0,
      "end_time": 176706.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176706.0,
      "end_time": 179606.0,
      "text": "The 15 minutes drive turned into 35 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180760.0,
      "end_time": 182886.0,
      "text": "I suggested to the gentleman that I need to get back"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182886.0,
      "end_time": 185896.0,
      "text": "because there&#39;s a very important meeting that I need to attend."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185896.0,
      "end_time": 189577.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, what this man did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190107.0,
      "end_time": 192897.0,
      "text": "when I just suggested I need to get back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 192897.0,
      "end_time": 194466.0,
      "text": "shocked me to the core."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 195877.0,
      "end_time": 198217.0,
      "text": "I believe most of you would be shocked to the core"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 198217.0,
      "end_time": 200187.0,
      "text": "when I tell you what he did."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 200627.0,
      "end_time": 203221.0,
      "text": "This guy broke down crying like a baby."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 203631.0,
      "end_time": 206681.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think any of you would cry"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 206681.0,
      "end_time": 210267.0,
      "text": "the first day when you have possession of a slick, yellow Lamborghini,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 210267.0,
      "end_time": 212267.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re driving it for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 212267.0,
      "end_time": 215768.0,
      "text": "And these were tears of anguish. How do you know what tears they are?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 215768.0,
      "end_time": 218518.0,
      "text": "When tears are cold, they&#39;re tears of joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 218518.0,
      "end_time": 221392.0,
      "text": "When tears are warm, they&#39;re tears of pain and anguish."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 221392.0,
      "end_time": 222597.0,
      "text": "Check it out next time."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 222597.0,
      "end_time": 224890.0,
      "text": "When someone is crying, don&#39;t take a thermometer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 224890.0,
      "end_time": 226444.0,
      "text": "\"This is tears of joy!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 226444.0,
      "end_time": 229518.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t test on others, you can test it for yourself, you know."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 230528.0,
      "end_time": 232497.0,
      "text": "I asked him what had happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 233470.0,
      "end_time": 236767.0,
      "text": "This man, with great difficulty, spoke up"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 237487.0,
      "end_time": 243370.0,
      "text": "and said, \"Just three days back my wife has filed papers for divorce.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 243367.0,
      "end_time": 247510.0,
      "text": "He was driving a car - fancy car -"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 247510.0,
      "end_time": 249291.0,
      "text": "he loved his wife, his children loved his wife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 249291.0,
      "end_time": 252668.0,
      "text": "for some reason the wife had filed papers for divorce."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 252669.0,
      "end_time": 256335.0,
      "text": "And this fancy Lamborghini, expensive, high-end car"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 256334.0,
      "end_time": 258435.0,
      "text": "couldn&#39;t wipe his tears;"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 259495.0,
      "end_time": 264450.0,
      "text": "this fancy, expensive, plush car couldn&#39;t bring him any hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 265150.0,
      "end_time": 268483.0,
      "text": "While I was driving with him I was thinking to myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 268483.0,
      "end_time": 272133.0,
      "text": "\"God. Look at this gentleman, with all of the achievements that he has:"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 272133.0,
      "end_time": 276212.0,
      "text": "a first-class business, incredible amounts of money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 276833.0,
      "end_time": 279630.0,
      "text": "tremendous influence and affluence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 279630.0,
      "end_time": 281614.0,
      "text": "and with all of that he had,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 281614.0,
      "end_time": 284693.0,
      "text": "and the cherry on top of the cake was a Lamborghini:"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 284694.0,
      "end_time": 285924.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 285924.0,
      "end_time": 288854.0,
      "text": "Bugged. No hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 289435.0,
      "end_time": 291626.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, therefore I say"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 291626.0,
      "end_time": 293916.0,
      "text": "if you truly want to know how rich you are"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 293916.0,
      "end_time": 297420.0,
      "text": "then count all those things that you have that money cannot buy."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 297882.0,
      "end_time": 304742.0,
      "text": "Hope, love, respect, dignity, character, integrity, acceptance."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 305626.0,
      "end_time": 307959.0,
      "text": "Wealth is a very broad term."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 308789.0,
      "end_time": 312484.0,
      "text": "Money is not wealth. Money is just a part of wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 312888.0,
      "end_time": 314455.0,
      "text": "And you must have it obviously -"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 314455.0,
      "end_time": 316667.0,
      "text": "all of you are looking forward to having money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 316667.0,
      "end_time": 318143.0,
      "text": "and you must obviously have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 318143.0,
      "end_time": 320604.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s just a part of wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 320605.0,
      "end_time": 322947.0,
      "text": "February 2, 2005,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 323837.0,
      "end_time": 328327.0,
      "text": "I was lying in a monastery in an ashram on the wooden floor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 328327.0,
      "end_time": 332175.0,
      "text": "exhausted, tired from the anxiety last night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 333185.0,
      "end_time": 337480.0,
      "text": "and suddenly a fellow monk, one of my friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 337518.0,
      "end_time": 340895.0,
      "text": "came up to me and woke me up"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 342135.0,
      "end_time": 346513.0,
      "text": "saying, \"He&#39;s leaving. He&#39;s leaving!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 347889.0,
      "end_time": 353589.0,
      "text": "I got up, gathering myself together, rushing to go to the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 353589.0,
      "end_time": 360500.0,
      "text": "where my dear friend Stoka Krishna Das was leaving his body."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 361928.0,
      "end_time": 367489.0,
      "text": "Memories were flashing through my mind as I was rushing towards this room."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 367839.0,
      "end_time": 371420.0,
      "text": "He was a monk with me, we had stayed together."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 371690.0,
      "end_time": 375520.0,
      "text": "At a certain point, he had decided to move on and get married."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 376890.0,
      "end_time": 377151.0,
      "text": "He went out."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 377151.0,
      "end_time": 381771.0,
      "text": "He&#39;d taken a job at the hospital we run, as a librarian."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 381771.0,
      "end_time": 386130.0,
      "text": "He&#39;d just gotten married; his wife was pregnant."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 387210.0,
      "end_time": 391280.0,
      "text": "While the wife was pregnant, he was diagnosed with melanoma cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 392251.0,
      "end_time": 395471.0,
      "text": "He decided that he wanted to leave the body in the monastery"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 395471.0,
      "end_time": 397132.0,
      "text": "where he spent most of his time."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 397132.0,
      "end_time": 399701.0,
      "text": "We had brought him to our monastery."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 399701.0,
      "end_time": 403271.0,
      "text": "As the memories flashed in my mind as I was rushing there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 403682.0,
      "end_time": 407652.0,
      "text": "I remembered everyday I went to sing God&#39;s names to him on the harmonium."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 408432.0,
      "end_time": 410551.0,
      "text": "My tears filled the eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 411491.0,
      "end_time": 416301.0,
      "text": "As I cried, seeing a dear friend struggling with melanoma cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 417691.0,
      "end_time": 421792.0,
      "text": "Every single time I looked at him, my vision was blurred."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 422792.0,
      "end_time": 426120.0,
      "text": "Because it was someone so dear."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 426120.0,
      "end_time": 428894.0,
      "text": "Yet, this gentleman was amazing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 428894.0,
      "end_time": 430752.0,
      "text": "he had a beaming face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 431702.0,
      "end_time": 434782.0,
      "text": "all the excruciating pain that he went through"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 434782.0,
      "end_time": 437453.0,
      "text": "hadn&#39;t affected his determined resolve."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 437453.0,
      "end_time": 440643.0,
      "text": "Yeah, look at his face, look at that smile."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 440643.0,
      "end_time": 443835.0,
      "text": "No morphine was working on him."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 444245.0,
      "end_time": 446650.0,
      "text": "I realized: this stuff works."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 447475.0,
      "end_time": 449804.0,
      "text": "His wife had given birth to a baby girl;"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 450164.0,
      "end_time": 454393.0,
      "text": "they brought the baby girl right next to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 454863.0,
      "end_time": 457513.0,
      "text": "It was the last time she would see him;"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 457513.0,
      "end_time": 461673.0,
      "text": "it was the last time his wife would ever be with him."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 462184.0,
      "end_time": 463703.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 464673.0,
      "end_time": 466483.0,
      "text": "as I walked to the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 467843.0,
      "end_time": 470174.0,
      "text": "my guru Radhanath Swami,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 470174.0,
      "end_time": 472964.0,
      "text": "the author of the popular book The Journey Home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 472964.0,
      "end_time": 475825.0,
      "text": "was right next to him, giving him hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 475825.0,
      "end_time": 479365.0,
      "text": "I was astounded inside the little room, there were so many people."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 479365.0,
      "end_time": 482265.0,
      "text": "I was standing right next to him with my guru Radhanath Swami,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 482265.0,
      "end_time": 486538.0,
      "text": "outside were 450 members of our community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 486538.0,
      "end_time": 489850.0,
      "text": "all together chanting the names of God."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 489595.0,
      "end_time": 493185.0,
      "text": "What I saw here was a man who didn&#39;t have a Lamborghini."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 493195.0,
      "end_time": 495344.0,
      "text": "What I saw here was support."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 496350.0,
      "end_time": 498395.0,
      "text": "What I saw here was people:"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 498395.0,
      "end_time": 500717.0,
      "text": "people who were there to financially support him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 500718.0,
      "end_time": 502925.0,
      "text": "people who were there to medically support him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 502925.0,
      "end_time": 505329.0,
      "text": "people who were there to spiritually support him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 505329.0,
      "end_time": 507796.0,
      "text": "people who were there to emotionally support him."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 508237.0,
      "end_time": 511530.0,
      "text": "I was amazed"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 511683.0,
      "end_time": 513783.0,
      "text": "at the kind of support this man had."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 513783.0,
      "end_time": 515300.0,
      "text": "You know something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 515299.99999999994,
      "end_time": 517399.99999999994,
      "text": "when you&#39;re born, people love you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 517400.0,
      "end_time": 519189.0,
      "text": "and when you die, people love you;"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 519190.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520890.00000000006,
      "text": "in between you have to manage."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 520890.0,
      "end_time": 521956.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 521956.0,
      "end_time": 524357.0,
      "text": "And this man had managed truly well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 524357.0,
      "end_time": 527271.0,
      "text": "he&#39;d invested so much in relationships with his people"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 527271.0,
      "end_time": 529296.0,
      "text": "that when he was in dire need"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 530277.0,
      "end_time": 531837.0,
      "text": "people had come to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 531837.0,
      "end_time": 533980.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 533980.0,
      "end_time": 537887.0,
      "text": "yes, it is important for us to have support."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 538688.0,
      "end_time": 540539.0,
      "text": "Wealth doesn&#39;t just mean money."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 540539.0,
      "end_time": 542629.0,
      "text": "Wealth means money plus"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 543219.0,
      "end_time": 545889.0,
      "text": "people and support."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 546449.0,
      "end_time": 547539.0,
      "text": "One gentleman said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 547539.0,
      "end_time": 550547.0,
      "text": "do you know what&#39;s the difference between complete and finished?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 550547.0,
      "end_time": 553283.0,
      "text": "He said if you find the right partner, you&#39;re complete;"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 553283.0,
      "end_time": 555569.0,
      "text": "If you find the wrong partner, you&#39;re finished."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 555569.0,
      "end_time": 559358.0,
      "text": "But if you were caught with the wrong one by the right one: completely finished."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 559358.0,
      "end_time": 562257.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause) (Cheers)"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 562258.0,
      "end_time": 566419.0,
      "text": "I must tell you: we definitely need partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 566419.0,
      "end_time": 568189.0,
      "text": "we definitely need friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 568189.0,
      "end_time": 570908.0,
      "text": "we definitely need professional therapists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 570908.0,
      "end_time": 574600.0,
      "text": "we definitely need people who can support us."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 574600.0,
      "end_time": 577309.0,
      "text": "Therefore, I say if you wanted to know truly how rich you are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 577309.0,
      "end_time": 580588.0,
      "text": "drop a tear and see how many hands come forward to wipe that tear."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 580588.0,
      "end_time": 582247.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how rich you actually are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 582248.0,
      "end_time": 583388.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 583388.0,
      "end_time": 584738.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 585599.0,
      "end_time": 589129.0,
      "text": "Sanskrit is an amazing language."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 589129.0,
      "end_time": 592989.0,
      "text": "If people want to call someone a donkey in Sanskrit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 592989.0,
      "end_time": 594719.0,
      "text": "you say Vaishakhnandan."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 594719.0,
      "end_time": 596500.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 596500.0,
      "end_time": 598830.0,
      "text": "You want to know what you call ice cream in Sanskrit?"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 598831.0,
      "end_time": 602386.0,
      "text": "Dughdasharkarayuktahima ganagolagattu."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 602831.0,
      "end_time": 604840.0,
      "text": "And if you say mango ice cream, you&#39;d say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 604840.0,
      "end_time": 608420.0,
      "text": "Aamra dughdasharkarayuktahima ganagolagattu."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 608420.0,
      "end_time": 610760.0,
      "text": "It will melt before you place the order!"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 610760.0,
      "end_time": 612111.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 612111.0,
      "end_time": 615821.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m sure most of us love to eat ice cream. Yes, indeed."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 616931.0,
      "end_time": 619460.0,
      "text": "People who eat ice cream, it is good to eat ice cream"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 619460.0,
      "end_time": 621562.0,
      "text": "because the ideology behind the ice cream is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 622662.0,
      "end_time": 625202.0,
      "text": "enjoy your life before it melts."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 627222.0,
      "end_time": 630901.0,
      "text": "And then there is a candle where the ideology is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 630901.0,
      "end_time": 633120.0,
      "text": "give light to others before it melts."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 633120.0,
      "end_time": 634482.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 634482.0,
      "end_time": 637622.0,
      "text": "yes, the live world is full of ice creams;"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 638482.0,
      "end_time": 641121.0,
      "text": "what we need is candles."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 641652.0,
      "end_time": 644401.0,
      "text": "Yes, there was a gentleman here in this country, Chennai,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 644401.0,
      "end_time": 646992.0,
      "text": "Mr. Palam Kalyanasundaram,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 647492.0,
      "end_time": 650502.0,
      "text": "giving away each of his salary to educate the poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 651292.0,
      "end_time": 654730.0,
      "text": "He was recognized by the U.S., given an award,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 654730.0,
      "end_time": 658893.0,
      "text": "about five million American dollars, approximately 30 crore Indian Rupees."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 658893.0,
      "end_time": 661952.0,
      "text": "He gave away all of that money to educate the poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 662632.0,
      "end_time": 665252.0,
      "text": "How many of you are ready to be candles?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 666503.0,
      "end_time": 668174.0,
      "text": "Contact me later, I need a lot!"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 668174.0,
      "end_time": 670384.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 670384.0,
      "end_time": 673304.0,
      "text": "To be honest, we cannot be that extreme,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 673304.0,
      "end_time": 674924.0,
      "text": "selfless candles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 674924.0,
      "end_time": 679170.0,
      "text": "and just because we can&#39;t be candles should we continue being ice creams?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 680840.0,
      "end_time": 685373.0,
      "text": "Journey means move from being an ice cream to a candle."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 685374.0,
      "end_time": 688501.0,
      "text": "How many of you like to look beautiful?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 689181.0,
      "end_time": 691681.0,
      "text": "How many of you like to look handsome?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 692251.0,
      "end_time": 695944.0,
      "text": "Those who are not raising their hands, they think they&#39;re already beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 695945.0,
      "end_time": 696955.0,
      "text": "I must tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 696955.0,
      "end_time": 700535.0,
      "text": "a teacher wrote down on the whiteboard: I am beautiful. \"Which tense is it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 700535.0,
      "end_time": 704105.0,
      "text": "The student said,\"Past tense, Madam.\" Visible beauty just goes away."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 704105.0,
      "end_time": 706220.0,
      "text": "One of my friends, ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 706220.0,
      "end_time": 708582.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to introduce you to a very handsome guy."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 708582.0,
      "end_time": 712652.0,
      "text": "One of my friends, Prem Raheja, wonderful man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 713532.0,
      "end_time": 715637.0,
      "text": "from a well-to-do, high middle-class family."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 716870.0,
      "end_time": 716992.0,
      "text": "This man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 718172.0,
      "end_time": 722462.0,
      "text": "his accountant&#39;s daughter stood first in the KEM medical college"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 722462.0,
      "end_time": 724685.0,
      "text": "and wanted to go the U.S to study"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 724685.0,
      "end_time": 728116.0,
      "text": "and didn&#39;t have any money, didn&#39;t have a sponsor for the visa."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 728116.0,
      "end_time": 730136.0,
      "text": "He sponsored her visa;"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 730136.0,
      "end_time": 733245.0,
      "text": "paid for her tuition fee, paid for the travel fee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 733245.0,
      "end_time": 737846.0,
      "text": "all of his staff, paid for the fees of all the children of his staff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 737846.0,
      "end_time": 740897.0,
      "text": "paid for the house of every single staff member,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 740897.0,
      "end_time": 743966.0,
      "text": "paid for the marriages of the every single person"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 743966.0,
      "end_time": 746580.0,
      "text": "in his staff&#39;s family."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 746468.0,
      "end_time": 749876.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s amazing is no one ever even knew."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 749876.0,
      "end_time": 753976.0,
      "text": "And there are so many such people across the country and across the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 753976.0,
      "end_time": 760106.0,
      "text": "who are trying to move from being an ice cream to being a candle."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 760106.0,
      "end_time": 761623.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 761623.0,
      "end_time": 765153.0,
      "text": "if you truly want to know how handsome you are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 765153.0,
      "end_time": 767363.0,
      "text": "just extend your \"hand\" to \"some,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 767363.0,
      "end_time": 770327.0,
      "text": "and you will definitely be considered to be extremely handsome."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 770327.0,
      "end_time": 772238.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not about the looks, which fade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 772238.0,
      "end_time": 774372.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s definitely about how we help others."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 774372.0,
      "end_time": 776286.0,
      "text": "It is important for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 776286.0,
      "end_time": 782236.0,
      "text": "that wealth is equal to money + people + purpose in life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 782236.0,
      "end_time": 784846.0,
      "text": "to serve, share and contribute."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 785299.0,
      "end_time": 789738.0,
      "text": "It was July 9, 2009."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 790108.0,
      "end_time": 792858.0,
      "text": "I had just returned from England, London."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 792858.0,
      "end_time": 794919.0,
      "text": "As I got back from London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 796590.0,
      "end_time": 798100.0,
      "text": "it was half one in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 798580.0,
      "end_time": 801650.0,
      "text": "for some reason my telephone was on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 801650.0,
      "end_time": 802345.0,
      "text": "cellular phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 804355.0,
      "end_time": 805505.0,
      "text": "My phone rang."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 807530.0,
      "end_time": 811920.0,
      "text": "My mind started going into guesses:"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 813420.0,
      "end_time": 814959.0,
      "text": "Who could it be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 815310.0,
      "end_time": 817959.0,
      "text": "My mom had rung me up."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 817959.0,
      "end_time": 820390.0,
      "text": "As I picked up the phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 821509.0,
      "end_time": 825179.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t want to hear the news that my father had gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 826500.0,
      "end_time": 828440.0,
      "text": "He was diagnosed with Parkinson&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 828441.0,
      "end_time": 830701.0,
      "text": "Just before I had traveled to London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 830701.0,
      "end_time": 833701.0,
      "text": "I had gone and seen him; he was bed ridden."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 833701.0,
      "end_time": 836449.0,
      "text": "From all the way as I&#39;d become a monk till now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 836449.0,
      "end_time": 838709.0,
      "text": "it had been an amazing journey for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 838709.0,
      "end_time": 842481.0,
      "text": "Hard in the beginning, definitely appreciated later."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 845860.0,
      "end_time": 847262.0,
      "text": "My dad had gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 848201.0,
      "end_time": 851592.0,
      "text": "I drove from Mumbai, it was pouring cats and dogs."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 853211.0,
      "end_time": 854870.0,
      "text": "The cremation was done."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 855802.0,
      "end_time": 860336.0,
      "text": "The next day I went to the crematorium,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 860799.0,
      "end_time": 863218.0,
      "text": "and what came in my hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 864890.0,
      "end_time": 865539.0,
      "text": "was a pot."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 868542.0,
      "end_time": 870197.0,
      "text": "A pot of ashes."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 872813.0,
      "end_time": 875513.0,
      "text": "As I held this pot of ashes in my hands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 877520.0,
      "end_time": 880633.0,
      "text": "I was stunned, shocked, couldn&#39;t think for a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 880633.0,
      "end_time": 884973.0,
      "text": "And this is 2009, I took this life as a monk in 1996"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 884973.0,
      "end_time": 887372.0,
      "text": "after having worked at Hewlett Packard."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 887373.0,
      "end_time": 888813.0,
      "text": "And as I was now there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 888813.0,
      "end_time": 890530.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m wondering:"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 890773.0,
      "end_time": 894373.0,
      "text": "is this my father?"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 896433.0,
      "end_time": 901144.0,
      "text": "Is this what&#39;s left out of my father?"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 901713.0,
      "end_time": 904934.0,
      "text": "God heard all what I&#39;d spoken, read, heard and spoken"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 904934.0,
      "end_time": 908204.0,
      "text": "in so many different forums including the British Parliament"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 910734.0,
      "end_time": 914840.0,
      "text": "had dawned upon me suddenly in that one moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 915674.0,
      "end_time": 917184.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s all gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 918714.0,
      "end_time": 920780.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll tell you something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 920588.0,
      "end_time": 923548.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s quite amazing how these sobering moments are."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 924115.0,
      "end_time": 927304.0,
      "text": "They bring to your heart those important priorities"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 927304.0,
      "end_time": 930353.0,
      "text": "which truly matter to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 930354.0,
      "end_time": 932201.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 932606.0,
      "end_time": 936546.0,
      "text": "you all have to evaluate what is of importance to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 936546.0,
      "end_time": 937798.0,
      "text": "What are we going to hold?"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 937798.0,
      "end_time": 940376.0,
      "text": "Grudges? Anger? What?"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 941496.0,
      "end_time": 944956.0,
      "text": "When we go we need to leave a legacy behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 945585.0,
      "end_time": 948276.0,
      "text": "and not just leave a legacy behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 948276.0,
      "end_time": 953960.0,
      "text": "When we go we must carry something along with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 953828.0,
      "end_time": 957639.0,
      "text": "On my way to London, on the flight, British Airways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 959170.0,
      "end_time": 962847.0,
      "text": "I had a mango milkshake bottle with me in the lunch pack."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 963663.0,
      "end_time": 967270.0,
      "text": "And at the X-ray machine as the mango milkshake passed through it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 967270.0,
      "end_time": 970180.0,
      "text": "the security guard said, \"Sir, this can&#39;t go ahead.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 970180.0,
      "end_time": 972737.0,
      "text": "I asked him, \"Why?\" He said, \"There&#39;s liquid in it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 972737.0,
      "end_time": 974896.0,
      "text": "I said, \"This is not liquid, this is sublime.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 974897.0,
      "end_time": 976158.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 976158.0,
      "end_time": 979680.0,
      "text": "He said, \"What is sublime?\" \"This is mango milkshake, sir.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 979680.0,
      "end_time": 983664.0,
      "text": "\"One liter of steel bottle.\" \"Sorry sir, only 100 ml is allowed.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 985404.0,
      "end_time": 988284.0,
      "text": "So I said, \"I&#39;ll throw it away,\" but I won&#39;t give it to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 988284.0,
      "end_time": 989734.0,
      "text": "\"Let me take it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 989734.0,
      "end_time": 990849.0,
      "text": "So I found someone -"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 990849.0,
      "end_time": 994309.0,
      "text": "I know someone the airport, he took me out and we gave it to the beggar -"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 994309.0,
      "end_time": 995639.0,
      "text": "and came back."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 995639.0,
      "end_time": 1001437.0,
      "text": "As I boarded the flight I put on my laptop with one thought:"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1002520.0,
      "end_time": 1005752.0,
      "text": "when you board a flight you must know what you can take along."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1006140.0,
      "end_time": 1008145.0,
      "text": "Everything else is left behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1009460.0,
      "end_time": 1014760.0,
      "text": "And similarly, when the flight ends, you have to know what you can take along;"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1014760.0,
      "end_time": 1016931.0,
      "text": "and therefore, I must say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1017870.0,
      "end_time": 1020801.0,
      "text": "there is a need for a divine spiritual connection."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1021480.0,
      "end_time": 1024332.0,
      "text": "Yes, when the flight ends, there are three things we must do:"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1024339.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1026790.9999999999,
      "text": "not have anything in the mind left thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 1026790.0,
      "end_time": 1028264.0,
      "text": "\"Oh! I should have done that!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 1028260.0,
      "end_time": 1030874.0,
      "text": "Second, we leave a legacy behind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 1030880.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1035410.0000000001,
      "text": "and three, we have something to carry on, even if it&#39;s 100 ml,"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 1035410.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1036820.0000000001,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 1036819.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1041206.9999999999,
      "text": "but it will be allowed with us as we move on;"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 1041200.0,
      "end_time": 1043519.0,
      "text": "and thus I say what makes life complete:"
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 1043520.0,
      "end_time": 1045778.0,
      "text": "Wealth makes life complete."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 1045780.0,
      "end_time": 1051511.0,
      "text": "Be super wealthy, have a lot of money, no problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 1052130.0,
      "end_time": 1055391.0,
      "text": "Be super wealthy, have a lot of support."
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 1056600.0,
      "end_time": 1057222.0,
      "text": "Be super wealthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 1057220.0,
      "end_time": 1061518.0,
      "text": "have a lot of purposes to move from an ice cream to a candle and share."
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 1061790.0,
      "end_time": 1064559.0,
      "text": "Be super wealthy, by leaving a legacy behind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 1064560.0,
      "end_time": 1070547.0,
      "text": "and having something that you can carry along with you as the flight lands."
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 1070550.0,
      "end_time": 1071874.0,
      "text": "Ladies and gentlemen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 1071870.0,
      "end_time": 1074110.0,
      "text": "I must thank all of you for your kind attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "start_time": 1074110.0,
      "end_time": 1075289.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 332,
      "start_time": 1075290.0,
      "end_time": 1076859.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}